 nam govore da uloga laika u svijetu je posvećivanje svijeta,

1201
00:59:28,320 --> 00:59:31,320
 naših obitelji, naših poslova.

1202
00:59:31,320 --> 00:59:37,320
 I često se mislimo da i previše razmišljamo o tome kakve su stvari u crkvi,

1203
00:59:37,320 --> 00:59:41,320
 tko šta radi u crkvi, tko čita, tko je ministrant.

1204
00:59:41,320 --> 00:59:44,320
 Al to nije naš posao, to je posao svećenika.

1205
00:59:44,320 --> 00:59:48,320
 Naš posao je posvećivanje struktura, posvećivanje svijeta.

1206
00:59:48,320 --> 00:59:52,320
 I čini to kao ovdje u pubovima, na javnim prostorima.

1207
00:59:52,320 --> 00:59:56,320
 So to finish, we have a talent in music,

1208
00:59:56,320 --> 00:59:59,320
 and as you hear I have a talent in marketing and politics.

1209
00:59:59,320 --> 01:00:04,320
 But I am 100% sure that there are many more talents here.

1210
01:00:04,320 --> 01:00:10,320
 and even though it seems hard, like to get into politics for me was crazy,

1211
01:00:10,320 --> 01:00:15,320
 because it was completely opposite to what everyone else was doing.

1212
01:00:15,320 --> 01:00:20,320
 But now we are after 8 years starting to see some good things.

1213
01:00:20,320 --> 01:00:26,320
 And to finish, we both have talent in music,

1214
01:00:26,320 --> 01:00:29,320
 and I also have talent in marketing and politics.

1215
01:00:29,320 --> 01:00:34,320
 And I think that here we have a lot more talent than that.

1216
01:00:34,320 --> 01:00:38,320
 And after 8 years, when I started politics,

1217
01:00:38,320 --> 01:00:41,320
 it was a great deal with everything that people said.

1218
01:00:41,320 --> 01:00:45,320
 But today, after 8 years, we will see the first applause.

1219
01:00:45,320 --> 01:00:48,320
 Thank you.

1220
01:00:48,320 --> 01:00:49,320
 Thank you.

1221
01:00:49,320 --> 01:00:50,320
 Thank you.

1222
01:00:50,320 --> 01:00:51,320
 Christian.

